    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the credibility plan for a Class II device at MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met across all five operating points evaluated.",
